using populate for linking models
 i.e. joining table 
 or reference documents in other collections

 Syntax --
 populate(which_model/object_u_want_to_update ,fields_u_want_to_bring_in(specify fields without comma ))

 jis model se populate krna h wo inside
 jis k ander krna h outside

 eg--.populate("products.product","name price")


Route when one  model is based on the other model----

 